                <h1>Discover the Wonders of Bourbon: Flavor, History & Cocktails</h1>
                <p>Bourbon is a distinct American whiskey, known for its rich, caramel flavor and smooth finish. Made primarily from corn, bourbon must be aged in new charred oak barrels, which impart unique notes of vanilla and spice. Enjoyed neat, on the rocks, or in classic cocktails, bourbon is a versatile spirit cherished by many.</p>
